<p align="center" style = " font-size:30px; color: #E8E8E8 ;border: 50px solid white;
    padding: 60px;  ">	
    <i>Grazhdanskaya Oborona (Civil defence,Gr. On. or TH) - Soviet and Russian rock group,
 founded on November 8, 
1984 in Omsk by Yegor Letov and Konstantin Ryabinov,
 the most prominent representative of the Siberian punk rock.

 The music at the initial stage was a punk rock with a strong garage influence,

 preserved throughout the creative activity of the group, 
and in the 1990s,      
 her style shifted towards psychedelic rock.

 "Civil defense" was one of the most influential punk rock groups of the USSR and Russia.
   
The group disbanded in 2008 after the death of Yegor Letov.</i> </p>



